---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DevDocs - Release Notes</title>
    <meta name="description" content="DevTools SDK release notes and documentation.">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #e4e4e7;
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .sidebar {
            width: 260px;
            background: #16162a;
            border-right: 1px solid #2d2d44;
            position: fixed;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .sidebar-header {
            padding: 0 20px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #2d2d44;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .sidebar-header h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .sidebar-header .version {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6366f1;
            background: #2d2d44;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        
        .nav-section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        .nav-section h3 {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #71717a;
            padding: 0 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .nav-section a {
            display: block;
            color: #a1a1aa;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        
        .nav-section a:hover { background: #2d2d44; color: #fff; }
        .nav-section a.active { background: #6366f1; color: #fff; }
        
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 260px;
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px 60px;
            max-width: 1000px;
        }
        
        .changelog h1 { font-size: 36px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        
        .changelog .release-date { color: #71717a; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        
        .changelog h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #2d2d44;
        }
        
        .changelog ul { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        
        .changelog ul li {
            padding: 12px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #d4d4d8;
        }
        
        .changelog ul li::before {
            content: '•';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #6366f1;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .changelog code {
            font-family: 'Fira Code', 'Monaco', 'Consolas', monospace;
            background: #2d2d44;
            color: #f472b6;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .changelog ul li code { background: #6366f120; color: #a5b4fc; }
        .changelog h2:first-of-type { color: #10b981; }
        .changelog h2:nth-of-type(2) { color: #f59e0b; }
        .changelog h2:nth-of-type(3) { color: #ef4444; }
        .changelog h2:nth-of-type(4) { color: #6366f1; }
        
        .breaking-badge {
            background: #ef4444;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 10px;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        
        .deprecation-notice {
            background: #2d2d44;
            border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .deprecation-notice code { color: #fbbf24; }
        
        .version-selector {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .version-selector a {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: #2d2d44;
            color: #a1a1aa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .version-selector a.active { background: #6366f1; color: #fff; }
        
        .contributors {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #2d2d44;
            color: #71717a;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .contributors a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; }
        .contributors a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        
        .full-changelog-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .full-changelog-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        
        .install-command {
            background: #0d0d1a;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
            color: #4ade80;
        }
        
        .install-command .prompt { color: #6366f1; }
        
        footer {
            margin-left: 260px;
            padding: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #2d2d44;
            text-align: center;
            color: #71717a;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        footer a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-header">
            <h2>DevDocs</h2>
            <span class="version">v3.0.0</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="nav-section">
            <h3>Getting Started</h3>
            <a href="#">Introduction</a>
            <a href="#">Quick Start</a>
            <a href="#">Installation</a>
            <a href="#">Configuration</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="nav-section">
            <h3>Core Concepts</h3>
            <a href="#">Architecture</a>
            <a href="#">Authentication</a>
            <a href="#">API Reference</a>
            <a href="#">Database</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="nav-section">
            <h3>Resources</h3>
            <a href="#">Changelog</a>
            <a href="#" class="active">Release Notes</a>
            <a href="#">Migration Guide</a>
            <a href="#">Contributing</a>
        </div>
    </aside>
    
    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="version-selector">
            <a href="#" class="active">v3.0</a>
            <a href="#">v2.5</a>
            <a href="#">v2.0</a>
            <a href="#">v1.5</a>
            <a href="#">v1.0</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="changelog">
            <h1>Release Notes - Version 3.0</h1>
            <p class="release-date">Released on March 10, 2026</p>
            
            <div class="install-command">
                <span class="prompt">$</span> npm install @devtools/sdk@3.0.0
            </div>
            
            <h2>What's New</h2>
            
            <ul>
                <li>Added <code>newFeature()</code> function to enable real-time collaboration between team members. This allows multiple users to edit documents simultaneously with instant synchronization.</li>
                <li>Introduced dark mode support - toggle available in settings panel</li>
                <li>Performance improvements: <code>query optimization</code> reduced load times by 40%</li>
                <li>New dashboard widgets for analytics</li>
                <li>Custom webhook support with <code>payload.signature</code> validation</li>
                <li>Added support for GraphQL subscriptions</li>
                <li>New CLI commands for automated deployments</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2>Bug Fixes</h2>
            
            <ul>
                <li>Fixed issue where <code>saveDocument()</code> would fail on files larger than 10MB</li>
                <li>Resolved memory leak in the notification system</li>
                <li>Fixed cross-browser compatibility issues with Safari</li>
                <li>Addressed <code>undefined</code> error when accessing user preferences</li>
                <li>Fixed WebSocket disconnection on mobile devices</li>
                <li>Resolved race condition in the caching layer</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2>Breaking Changes <span class="breaking-badge">BREAKING</span></h2>
            
            <div class="deprecation-notice">
                <strong>Migration Required:</strong> The following changes require updates to your codebase. Please see the <a href="#" style="color:#a5b4fc">Migration Guide</a> for detailed instructions.
            </div>
            
            <ul>
                <li>API endpoint <code>/v2/users/profile</code> now requires authentication header</li>
                <li>Deprecated <code>legacyExport()</code> - use <code>newExport()</code> instead</li>
                <li>Minimum Node.js version increased to 18.x</li>
                <li>Configuration file format changed from YAML to JSON</li>
                <li>Removed deprecated <code>connect()</code> method - use <code>connectAsync()</code></li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2>Under the Hood</h2>
            
            <ul>
                <li>Upgraded database driver to <code>pg@14.0.0</code></li>
                <li>Refactored authentication module for better security</li>
                <li>Added comprehensive logging with <code>structuredLogger</code> for debugging</li>
                <li>Migrated from REST to gRPC for internal services</li>
                <li>Improved type definitions for TypeScript users</li>
            </ul>
            
            <a href="#" class="full-changelog-link">View full changelog →</a>
            
            <div class="contributors">
                <p>Thanks to our contributors: <a href="#">@johndoe</a>, <a href="#">@jane smith</a>, <a href="#">@devteam</a>, <a href="#">@alexchen</a>, <a href="#">@sarahk</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 DevTools Inc. <a href="#">Documentation</a> | <a href="#">Support</a> | <a href="#">Status</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
